abstract: Driven column review of 2016 Toyota Tacoma midsize pickup truck.
lead_paragraph: With an upgraded structure, a reduction in noise and more, the 2016 model is a far better truck than the one it replaces.

headline.main: Video Review: Toyota Tacoma Adds Machismo, but Retains Its Reliability
headline.print_headline: An Upgraded Toyota Tacoma Adds Machismo, but Retains Its Reliability
